Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.55,0:43:54.64,jp,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}巡り会わせた　意味さえ全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.56,0:44:05.52,jp,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an7}I promise to　あの空の向こう側へと
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.66,0:44:19.39,jp,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}今もまだ聞こえてる　君の果てなき愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.97,0:44:32.34,jp,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}今はただ　運命の無情を抱いまま
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.27,0:44:34.93,jp,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}'Cause of you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.28,0:44:45.26,jp,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}もう行きなさい　信じていいから　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.54,0:44:56.46,jp,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,7000)\an7}何処にいても想いを　唱って
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.63,0:43:47.75,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}You save 注意到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.55,0:43:54.64,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}连同我们邂逅的所有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.56,0:44:05.52,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\an3}I promise to 飞往那天空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.66,0:44:19.39,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}你那无尽的爱语如今尚环绕耳边
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.97,0:44:32.34,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}但现在只能接受命运的无情
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.27,0:44:34.93,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}'Cause of you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.28,0:44:45.26,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}我这就起程了 能相信你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.54,0:44:56.46,cn,Alchemy+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,7000)\an3}无论身处何方我都会歌颂这份思念
